question.text: Why i topup via tng but not in my joker wallet?
variations: No amount added

languages.en: Why i topup via tng but not in my joker wallet?
languages.ms: Kenapa saya topup melalui tng tetapi tidak masuk ke dalam dompet joker saya?

detailed.en: If you have tried to top up using Touch 'n Go (TNG) and it did not enter your Joker wallet, there may be several reasons. If you used Fast Payment (FPX), ensure you selected TNG eWallet in the payment section and wait 1-3 minutes for the system to automatically verify the transaction. If it still does not enter after 3 minutes, please send the FPX transaction receipt to live chat for review. If you used DuitNow Transfer via TNG, ensure you selected DuitNow to a bank account number, not a regular eWallet transfer. Upload the transaction receipt manually to the top-up page in the app and wait 3-10 minutes for the system to verify. If there are still issues, try changing the internet network (WiFi/Data), check if TNG is under maintenance, or try other methods like ATM/Transfer. If it still does not work, reply to us in live chat for further assistance.
detailed.ms: Jika anda telah cuba top up menggunakan Touch 'n Go (TNG) dan ia tidak masuk ke dalam dompet Joker anda, mungkin ada beberapa sebab. Jika anda menggunakan Fast Payment (FPX), pastikan anda memilih TNG eWallet dalam bahagian pembayaran dan tunggu 1-3 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan transaksi secara automatik. Jika selepas 3 minit ia masih tidak masuk, sila hantar resit transaksi FPX ke live chat untuk semakan. Jika anda menggunakan DuitNow Transfer melalui TNG, pastikan anda memilih DuitNow ke nombor akaun bank, bukan pemindahan eWallet biasa. Muat naik resit transaksi secara manual ke halaman top-up dalam aplikasi dan tunggu 3-10 minit untuk sistem mengesahkan. Jika masih ada masalah, cuba tukar rangkaian internet (WiFi/Data), semak jika TNG sedang dalam penyelenggaraan, atau cuba kaedah lain seperti ATM/Pindahan. Jika masih tidak berjaya, balas kepada kami di live chat untuk bantuan lanjut.

languages.en: How to top up using ATM/Transfer or Fast Payment (FPX)?

detailed.en: To top up using ATM/Transfer, use Instant Transfer/DuitNow, enter the correct company account number and amount, write your JOKER ID in 'Recipient Reference', and upload the receipt to the top-up page in the app. The process takes 3-10 minutes.
